Stargate Atlantis Season 05 Episode 17 - Infection

Reencode of CTU release for smaller file size. Had a problem with my encoder, now fixed. Using a different filter on this one, I think I should turn down it&amp;#039;s strength a tiny bit on a next release. Although it&amp;#039;s set pretty low already.


